---
import { Carousel } from "webcoreui/astro";
import "../../styles/projects.css";
---

<div id="visuallog" class="project-card">
  <div class="space-y-4 md:landscape:w-1/2">
    <h3 class="font-bold">VisualLog</h3>
    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-400">A GUI-based text logging app</h4>
    <ul class="font-bold text-blue-400 list-disc list-inside">
      <li>First Commit: 2024-07-24</li>
      <li>Final Commit: 2024-08-23</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Built in C# using WPF. This project shows my application of
      Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) and Model–View–ViewModel GUI
      architecture (MVVM).
      <br /><br />
      A string of characters can be input and saved, alongside the current time into
      a json file with customizable save path. The messages stored in said file will
      then be displayed through GUI.
    </p>

    <p>
      For more details, visit <a
        class="text-blue-400 font-semibold"
        href="https://github.com/ilialyl/VisualLog"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">VisualLog</a
      >
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="md:landscape:w-1/2">
    <Carousel items={3}>
      <li>
        <a
          href="projects/visual_log_1.png"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="./projects/visual_log_1.png" /></a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="projects/visual_log_2.png"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="./projects/visual_log_2.png" /></a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="projects/visual_log_3.png"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="./projects/visual_log_4.png" /></a
        >
      </li>
    </Carousel>
  </div>
</div>
